========
Flowbber
========

Flowbber is a generic tool and framework that allows to execute custom
pipelines for data gathering, publishing and analysis.


Documentation
=============

    https://flowbber.readthedocs.io


Changelog
=========

1.0.0 (2017-08-30)
------------------

New
~~~

- Initial version.


TODO
====
